room_title: Escape room "Doomed to Die" by Southern Pines Escape in Southern Pines
review: Great experience! Great staff! Thanks for a wonderful time with my son. We enjoyed "Dial D for death" and look forward to trying another one in the future!

room_title: Escape room "Doomed to Die" by Southern Pines Escape in Southern Pines
review: We were there yesterday and had a blast! Dial 'D' for murder was a challenge that kept us hopping. We left that room a mess! We will definitely be back! Thanks for having us and letting us have a few clues!

room_title: Escape room "Doomed to Die" by Southern Pines Escape in Southern Pines
review: What an awesome 1st time experience at the Southern Pines Escape Room! Our team had a blast, we escaped the Dial "D" for Death room and beat a record! Our game master, Alyssa was amazing! We cannot wait to go back again to try out the other rooms!
